<html xmlns:o='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office' xmlns:w='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40'><head><meta charset='utf-8'><title>Text To Word</title></head><body><p>⭐ <strong>DAY 1</strong></p>
<p><strong>Character Improvement &ndash; Awareness &amp; Focus</strong></p>
<p><strong>Mindfulness breathing</strong></p>
<p>Sit comfortably, close your eyes. Inhale 4 counts &rarr; Hold 2 &rarr; Exhale 6. Bring focus back whenever thoughts wander.</p>
<p><strong>Gratitude journal</strong></p>
<p>Write 3 specific things you're grateful for. Example: &ldquo;I&rsquo;m grateful someone helped me today.&rdquo;</p>
<p><strong>Goal review / prioritization</strong></p>
<p>List today&rsquo;s tasks &rarr; circle top 3 &rarr; visualize completing them.</p>
<p><strong>Reflection</strong></p>
<p>Recall moments you stayed calm or disciplined. Write 1&ndash;2 lines and note what to improve tomorrow.</p>
<p><strong>Speaker Training &ndash; Voice &amp; Clarity</strong></p>
<p><strong>Warm-up</strong></p>
<p>Hum 2 minutes, do 2&ndash;3 tongue twisters slowly &rarr; faster, deep breathing warm-up.</p>
<p><strong>Pronunciation drill</strong></p>
<p>Choose 5 words you mispronounce; say each clearly 5 times.</p>
<p><strong>Voice projection</strong></p>
<p>Stand tall and read a paragraph aloud, projecting without shouting.</p>
<p><strong>Record &amp; review</strong></p>
<p>Record 1&ndash;2 minutes. Note clarity, speed, confidence.</p>
<p><strong>English &amp; Urdu &ndash; Pronunciation Basics</strong></p>
<p><strong>English tricky words</strong></p>
<p>Pick 5 difficult English words (through, enough). Repeat 5&times; slowly with clean sounds.</p>
<p><strong>Urdu tricky words</strong></p>
<p>Practice 5 words like خواب، مشکل، فیصلہ. Speak clearly.</p>
<p><strong>Tongue twisters</strong></p>
<p>English + Urdu twisters. Repeat slow &rarr; fast while keeping clarity.</p>
<p><strong>Recording</strong></p>
<p>Record 1&ndash;2 minutes speaking both languages; identify unclear words.</p>
<p><strong>Weight Loss &ndash; Cardio &amp; Movement</strong></p>
<p><strong>Brisk walk/jog</strong></p>
<p>10 minutes brisk walk or jogging in place.</p>
<p><strong>HIIT</strong></p>
<p>1 min jumping jacks &rarr; 30 sec rest &rarr; 1 min squats &rarr; repeat.</p>
<p><strong>Core workout</strong></p>
<p>30 sec plank &rarr; 30 sec rest &rarr; 30 sec crunches &rarr; repeat.</p>
<p><strong>Hydration + reflection</strong></p>
<p>Drink water, note energy + hunger levels.</p>
<p><strong>Self-Care &ndash; Physical Health</strong></p>
<p><strong>Stretching</strong></p>
<p>5&ndash;10 minutes full-body stretch.</p>
<p><strong>Hydration</strong></p>
<p>Drink one full glass of water.</p>
<p><strong>Light exercise</strong></p>
<p>10-minute bodyweight routine or walk.</p>
<p><strong>Body reflection</strong></p>
<p>Notice tension, flexibility, and energy.</p>
<p><strong>Skin &amp; Teeth &ndash; Cleansing &amp; Care</strong></p>
<p><strong>Face washing</strong></p>
<p>Use a gentle cleanser and pat dry.</p>
<p><strong>Moisturizer + sunscreen</strong></p>
<p>Apply moisturizer, use sunscreen if going outdoors.</p>
<p><strong>Teeth brushing + flossing</strong></p>
<p>Brush 2 minutes. Floss once.</p>
<p><strong>Hydration reflection</strong></p>
<p>Drink water and notice skin freshness.</p>
<p><strong>Eyelash Care &ndash; Cleaning &amp; Prep</strong></p>
<p><strong>Gentle cleansing</strong></p>
<p>Remove makeup carefully using mild cleanser.</p>
<p><strong>Eyelid massage</strong></p>
<p>1&ndash;2 minutes gentle circular massage.</p>
<p><strong>Apply oil (castor/coconut)</strong></p>
<p>Use a clean brush to apply castor or coconut oil.</p>
<p><strong>Reflection</strong></p>
<p>Check for irritation and overall softness.</p>
<p><strong>Skill Learning &ndash; Introduction</strong></p>
<p><strong>Overview of skill</strong></p>
<p>Understand what the skill is, its purpose, and tools used.</p>
<p><strong>Basic concepts</strong></p>
<p>Study the base rules or principles.</p>
<p><strong>Mini practice</strong></p>
<p>Do a very small exercise related to the skill.</p>
<p><strong>Reflection</strong></p>
<p>Write 2 things learned + 1 difficulty.</p>
<p><strong>Front-End Dev &ndash; HTML Basics</strong></p>
<p><strong>Structure tags</strong></p>
<p>Build a simple HTML file using `&lt;html&gt;, &lt;head&gt;, &lt;body&gt;`.</p>
<p><strong>Links &amp; images</strong></p>
<p>Add `&lt;a&gt;` and `&lt;img&gt;` with alt text.</p>
<p><strong>Tables &amp; forms</strong></p>
<p>Make a 2&ndash;3 row table + a basic name/email form.</p>
<p><strong>Review</strong></p>
<p>Open in browser and fix issues.</p>
<p><strong>Backend Dev &ndash; Environment Setup</strong></p>
<p><strong>Install Node.js</strong></p>
<p>Install and verify using `node -v`.</p>
<p><strong>Run first script</strong></p>
<p>Create a simple JS file and run `node filename.js`.</p>
<p><strong>Learn commands</strong></p>
<p>Practice console.log and basics.</p>
<p><strong>Practice</strong></p>
<p>Write a small script using variables/functions.</p>
<p><strong>Money Roadmap &ndash; Skill Identification</strong></p>
<p><strong>Assess skills</strong></p>
<p>List your strengths and interests.</p>
<p><strong>Research markets</strong></p>
<p>Check freelancing sites to see demand.</p>
<p><strong>Select main skill</strong></p>
<p>Choose the skill you want to monetize first.</p>
<p><strong>Set goals</strong></p>
<p>Write your financial target and weekly plan.</p>
<p><strong>⭐ DAY 2</strong></p>
<p><strong>Character &ndash; Discipline &amp; Time Management</strong></p>
<p><strong>Morning planning</strong></p>
<p>Write 3 mini, achievable goals.</p>
<p><strong>Task sprint</strong></p>
<p>Work 10 mins straight on 1 task without distractions.</p>
<p><strong>Self-control drill</strong></p>
<p>Avoid one temptation (phone, snacks) for 10 mins.</p>
<p><strong>Evening review</strong></p>
<p>Write where you were disciplined and one thing to improve.</p>
<p><strong>Speaking &ndash; Confidence &amp; Posture</strong></p>
<p><strong>Power poses</strong></p>
<p>Stand confidently 2 minutes + say brief affirmations.</p>
<p><strong>Eye contact</strong></p>
<p>Practice talking while maintaining mirror eye contact.</p>
<p><strong>Emotion reading</strong></p>
<p>Read a small paragraph applying emotion variations.</p>
<p><strong>Reflection</strong></p>
<p>Note where confidence improved and what felt difficult.</p>
<p><strong>English &amp; Urdu &ndash; Vocabulary Day</strong></p>
<p><strong>English 5 new words</strong></p>
<p>Learn 5 new words, make and speak sentences.</p>
<p><strong>Urdu 5 new words</strong></p>
<p>Learn 5 Urdu words/phrases and speak sentences.</p>
<p><strong>Expressive reading</strong></p>
<p>Read English and Urdu texts focusing on tone and clarity.</p>
<p><strong>Reflection</strong></p>
<p>Write 2 improved English words + 2 Urdu words.</p>
<p><strong>Weight Loss &ndash; Strength &amp; Tone</strong></p>
<p><strong>Squats</strong></p>
<p>3 sets of 15.</p>
<p><strong>Push-ups</strong></p>
<p>3 sets of 10 (regular or knee).</p>
<p><strong>Lunges</strong></p>
<p>10 minutes lunges + calf raises.</p>
<p><strong>Stretching</strong></p>
<p>Full-body stretch for recovery.</p>
<p><strong>Self-Care &ndash; Mental Clarity</strong></p>
<p><strong>Breathing</strong></p>
<p>Slow 4&ndash;2&ndash;6 breathing.</p>
<p><strong>Journaline</strong></p>
<p>Write 3 thoughts or worries.</p>
<p><strong>Digital detox</strong></p>
<p>Stay off phone 10 minutes.</p>
<p><strong>Reflection</strong></p>
<p>Note distracting thoughts vs calming ones.</p>
<p><strong>Skin &amp; Teeth &ndash; Exfoliation Day</strong></p>
<p><strong>Face scrub</strong></p>
<p>Use gentle exfoliant.</p>
<p><strong>Mask</strong></p>
<p>Apply brightening mask (aloe/yogurt/honey).</p>
<p><strong>Teeth whitening</strong></p>
<p>Use whitening toothpaste or mild home remedy.</p>
<p><strong>Moisturizer</strong></p>
<p>Reapply moisturizer.</p>
<p><strong>Eyelash &ndash; Strengthening Day</strong></p>
<p><strong>Brushing</strong></p>
<p>Brush lashes with spoolie.</p>
<p><strong>Oil application</strong></p>
<p>Add castor or almond oil.</p>
<p><strong>Massage</strong></p>
<p>Massage eyelid for 1&ndash;2 mins.</p>
<p><strong>Avoid makeup</strong></p>
<p>Give lashes rest.</p>
<p><strong>Skill Learning &ndash; Practice Repetition</strong></p>
<p><strong>Review basics</strong></p>
<p>Go through yesterday&rsquo;s notes.</p>
<p><strong>Focus exercise</strong></p>
<p>Practice weak area for 5&ndash;10 mins.</p>
<p><strong>Feedback</strong></p>
<p>Compare results with tutorials.</p>
<p><strong>Reflection</strong></p>
<p>Write 1 improvement.</p>
<p><strong>Front-End &ndash; CSS Basics</strong></p>
<p><strong>Inline/internal CSS</strong></p>
<p>Style headings + paragraphs.</p>
<p><strong>Box model</strong></p>
<p>Test margin, padding, border.</p>
<p><strong>Text &amp; background styling</strong></p>
<p>Change colors, fonts, alignment.</p>
<p><strong>Review</strong></p>
<p>Refresh browser to check changes.</p>
<p><strong>Backend &ndash; JS Revision</strong></p>
<p><strong>Variables</strong></p>
<p>Practice let, const, var.</p>
<p><strong>Arrays &amp; objects</strong></p>
<p>Perform CRUD.</p>
<p><strong>Loops</strong></p>
<p>Use for/while loops.</p>
<p><strong>Practice</strong></p>
<p>Do a small JS exercise.</p>
<p><strong>Money Roadmap &ndash; Skill Learning</strong></p>
<p><strong>Learn core skill</strong></p>
<p>Watch short tutorial and practice.</p>
<p><strong>Daily practice</strong></p>
<p>Do one small related task.</p>
<p><strong>Portfolio samples</strong></p>
<p>Start building example work.</p>
<p><strong>Reflection</strong></p>
<p>Write daily progress.</p>
