<p>**Urdu accent**</p>
<p>Speak 2&ndash;3 Urdu sentences with clear rhythm.</p>
<p>**Emotion sentences**</p>
<p>Say 5 sentences in both languages with different emotions.</p>
<p>**Reflection**</p>
<p>Write what felt natural and what needs improvement.</p>
<p>---</p>
